# FPGA Auto project workspace ignore policy.
#
# Keep the repository source-first: generated Vivado/Vitis/simulation output is
# ignored, while project inputs are addable without per-project exceptions.

# Start closed so random generated files do not become visible by accident.
*
!*/
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!**/.gitkeep

# Project contracts and human-maintained metadata.
!**/fpga_auto.yml
!**/*.md
!**/*.txt
!**/*.json
!**/*.yml
!**/*.yaml
!**/README*
!**/LICENSE*

# HDL, constraints, verification, firmware, and project-local tooling.
!**/src/**
!**/tb/**
!**/constrs/**
!**/constraints/**
!**/include/**
!**/inc/**
!**/ip/**
!**/sw/**
!**/tools/**
!**/scripts/**
!**/tests/**

# Project-owned documentation and planning assets.
!**/md/**
!**/docs/**
!**/doc/**
!**/Presentation/**
!**/diagram_layout/**
!**/report_assets/**
!**/skills/**

# Generated FPGA_AUTO outputs.
**/output/
**/log/
**/logs/
**/vivado_project/
**/vitis/
**/tb_runtime/
**/UVM_report/
**/uvm_report/
**/.analysis/
**/trashLegacy/

# Xilinx/Vivado/Vitis generated workspaces and transient files.
**/.Xil/
**/.xsim/
**/xsim.dir/
**/.ip_user_files/
**/*.cache/
**/*.gen/
**/*.hw/
**/*.runs/
**/*.sim/
*.jou
*.log
*.pb
*.str
*.wdb
*.wcfg
*.vcd
*.fst
*.vpd
*.html
*.htm
*.rpt
*.dcp
*.bit
*.ltx
*.mmi
*.xsa
*.xpr
*.hwdef
dfx_runtime.txt
clockInfo.txt

# Verilator, native, and embedded build products.
**/obj_dir/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
compile_commands.json
*.o
*.obj
*.d
*.a
*.so
*.dll
*.exe
*.elf
*.map
*.lst
*.bin
*.hex

# Python/tool caches.
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Local editor, OS, browser-automation, and archive noise.
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.playwright-cli/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.tmp
*.bak
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.7z
